fields.name: Adjustments
fields.description: The amount of balance adjustment. The property is not available for ConsumptionCommitment lots.

fields.name: AdjustmentsInBillingCurrency
fields.description: The amount of balance adjustment in billing currency.

fields.name: BillingAccountDisplayName
fields.description: Name of the billing account.

fields.name: BillingAccountId
fields.description: Identifier of the billing account.

fields.name: BillingCurrency
fields.description: The billing currency of the event.

fields.name: BillingProfileDisplayName
fields.description: The display name of the billing profile for which the event happened. The property is only available for billing account of type MicrosoftCustomerAgreement.

fields.name: BillingProfileId
fields.description: The ID that uniquely identifies the billing profile for which the event happened. The property is only available for billing account of type MicrosoftCustomerAgreement.

fields.name: CanceledCredit
fields.description: Amount of canceled credit.

fields.name: Charges
fields.description: The amount of charges for events of type SettleCharges and PendingEligibleCharges.

fields.name: ChargesInBillingCurrency
fields.description: The amount of charges for events of type SettleCharges and PendingEligibleCharges in billing currency.

fields.name: ClosedBalance
fields.description: The balance after the event, Note: This will not be returned for Contributor Organization Type in Multi-Entity consumption commitment

fields.name: ClosedBalanceInBillingCurrency
fields.description: The balance in billing currency after the event, Note: This will not be returned for Contributor Organization Type in Multi-Entity consumption commitment

fields.name: CreditCurrency
fields.description: The credit currency of the event.

fields.name: CreditExpired
fields.description: The amount of expired credit or commitment for NewCredit or SettleCharges event.

fields.name: CreditExpiredInBillingCurrency
fields.description: The amount of expired credit or commitment for NewCredit or SettleCharges event in billing currency.

fields.name: Description
fields.description: The description of the event.

fields.name: ETag
fields.description: The eTag for the resource.

fields.name: EventType
fields.description: Identifies the type of the event.

fields.name: InvoiceNumber
fields.description: The number which uniquely identifies the invoice on which the event was billed. This will be empty for unbilled events.

fields.name: IsEstimatedBalance
fields.description: If true, the listed details are based on an estimation and it will be subjected to change.

fields.name: LotId
fields.description: The ID that uniquely identifies the lot for which the event happened.

fields.name: LotSource
fields.description: Identifies the source of the lot for which the event happened.

fields.name: NewCredit
fields.description: The amount of new credit or commitment for NewCredit or SettleCharges event.

fields.name: NewCreditInBillingCurrency
fields.description: The amount of new credit or commitment for NewCredit or SettleCharges event in billing currency.

fields.name: Reseller
fields.description: The reseller of the event.

fields.name: TransactionDate
fields.description: The date of the event.
